- visit and see what others are doing, communicate with them by leaving a message on their blogs or writing them mails;

- learning by yourself
- write and express your thoughts through all tools available to you: blog, forums, vedio broadcasting, chat; many technologies are under development now, stay tuned and be aware;
- we encourage you to look into what others have to say, and communicate with them;
- invent: this is a learning platform, and the essence of learning is using what you have learned to serve others. a great way to serve others is to invent something new.
